---
layout: base.njk
title: "404: Lost in the Crates | The Groove Library"
description: "Looks like this record skipped off the turntable. The page you're looking for can't be found."
permalink: /404.html
---

{# Hero Section #}
<section class="region region--xl bg-brand" aria-labelledby="error-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="center center--intrinsic flow flow--xl text-center">
      {# Animated vinyl record icon #}
      <div class="error-vinyl" aria-hidden="true">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-record-vinyl fa-6x text-inverse"></i>
      </div>

      <div class="flow flow--lg">
        <div class="flow flow--sm">
          <h1 id="error-heading" class="text-5xl text-inverse">
            404: Lost in the Crates
          </h1>
          <p class="text-2xl text-inverse">
            Looks like this record skipped off the turntable
          </p>
        </div>

        <p class="text-lg text-inverse opacity-90">
          We've been digging through the entire collection, but this page is nowhere to be found. <br>
          It might have been sampled, scratched out, or never pressed in the first place.
        </p>

        {# Funny music-themed suggestions #}
        <div class="error-suggestions flow flow--md">
          <p class="text-semibold text-inverse">While you're here, why not:</p>
          <ul class="error-list text-inverse">
            <li>
              <i class="fa-solid fa-record-vinyl fa-sm" aria-hidden="true"></i>
              Check if you spelled the URL correctly (no auto-tune for typos)
            </li>
            <li>
              <i class="fa-solid fa-compact-disc fa-sm" aria-hidden="true"></i>
              Head back to the homepage and start fresh
            </li>
            <li>
              <i class="fa-solid fa-tape fa-sm" aria-hidden="true"></i>
              Browse our collection instead of searching for lost grooves
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        {# Navigation buttons #}
        <div class="cluster cluster--lg justify-center">
          <a href="/" class="button button--primary text-inverse">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-house fa-sm" aria-hidden="true"></i>
            Back to Homepage
          </a>
          <a href="/easton-chop-up/" class="button button--secondary text-inverse">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-record-vinyl fa-sm" aria-hidden="true"></i>
            Browse Easton Chop Up
          </a>
        </div>

        {# Fun fact #}
        <div class="error-funfact">
          <p class="text-sm text-inverse opacity-75">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-lightbulb fa-sm" aria-hidden="true"></i>
            <em>Fun fact: 404 errors are named after room 404 at CERN, where the web was born. <br>
            No one knows what happened to room 404. It's probably on a 404 page too.</em>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# Alternative navigation section #}
<section class="region region--lg" aria-labelledby="nav-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="wrapper wrapper--narrow flow flow--xl text-center">
      <h2 id="nav-heading" class="text-3xl">
        Or explore these sections
      </h2>

      <div class="grid grid--2">
        {% for page in navigation.pages %}
          <a href="{{ page.url }}" class="error-nav-card">
            <div class="error-nav-card__icon">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-record-vinyl fa-2x" aria-hidden="true"></i>
            </div>
            <h3 class="error-nav-card__title">{{ page.title }}</h3>
            <p class="error-nav-card__arrow">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right fa-sm" aria-hidden="true"></i>
            </p>
          </a>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
